        public reactor.core.publisher.Flux<RxDocumentServiceResponse> processMessage(RxDocumentServiceRequest request)
        Description copied from interface: RxStoreModel
        Given the request, it returns an Observable of the response. The Observable upon subscription will execute the request and upon successful execution request returns a single RxDocumentServiceResponse. If the execution of the request fails it returns an error.
